 lord no.<br>It doesn't say Roleplaying. It doesnt say Roleplaying..<br>WHAT THE HELL..<br><br>It doesn't say Roleplaying.<br><br>It doesn't say Roleplaying.<br><br>Why doesn't it say roleplaying.. my OriginalArgument is hammered.<br>Looks like I'm the one that got owned on the Factor.<br><br>Even Verant has given up on us. Us the lost Children of Roleplaying.<br><br>The Opressive Powergamers have driven us into a Corner. They have taken from us what was ours, beat us into a corner. Destroyed our homeworld, raped and piullaged our land, backhanded our kid, knocked our team out the playoffs, badly dubbed anime, and hung us out to dry.<br><br>Why doesn't it say Roleplaying in Velious? I fully expected it to as I typed in the words. But it doesnt.<br><br>Just now, I remembered something that the Small tightknit Roleplaying community on Innoruuk said.<br><br>They said, with the Release of Kunark, Roleplaying began to Fade in favor for Uberisum and Powergaming.<br><br>I see it more clearly then I have ever seen it in my entire time playing Everquest.<br><br>They come, in shades begging for Equality, crying words of Racium and Biggotry, crying of Intolerance..<br><br>While, with their conversionary methods, and their way of Uberisum, they have taken the Rug right out from under the Roleplayers Legs, Beat his children infront of his face, pillaged and raped his land, and destroyed all that he holds dear.<br>In short, we are the Oppressed Few.<br><br>We are the pilgrums, who were oppressed because we were not allowed to pratice our religion.<br><br>We didn't leave our land because we wanted to.<br><br>We left our land because we had to.<br><br>We had to survive.<br><br>We had to live on.<br><br>We are the Oppressed Roleplayers. Oppressed by the Powergamers.<br>The Man. The Powergaming Man holds us down.<br>And soon, the Powergaming man will snuff us out.<br><br>The Roleplayer cannot escape the Powergaming man. He is too strong. His draw is too powerful. Those that do not assimilate into the Powergaming man's fold are overwhelemed and Destroyed.<br><br>I stood out infront of the Powergaming man, and I said, in a loud boustious voice.<br><br>'FUCK YOU~!'<br><br>And I was destroyed. My land was taken from me. My Sheep were eaten. I was booted from my land.<br><br>Then I saw a glimmer of Light.<br><br>Faint that it was, i still saw that Glimmer of Light.<br><br>Thank you Jaxy for providing that Glimmer of Light.<br>And I followed it.<br><br>And It lead me here.<br><br>To the promised Land.<br>The Promised Land of the Roleplayer.<br><br>We didn't have to worry about the Oppressive force of the Powergaming Man, for we were free from his Trynarry. I got new Sheep. I had new land that I could cultivate and grow fresh Beets from. I could finally have my Corn, I could raise some Chickens and fry them up. I love fried Chicken.<br><br>But the Powergaming man.. he is bored. He has no more Roleplayers to oppress. His Loot, his attude, his power means nothing if he cannot use it to dominate another.<br><br>If everyone is Uber, who will look up to him?<br><br>That glimmer of Light has brought the face of the Powergaming man to us here as well.<br><br>He stands up, bearing fangs and mighty claws.<br><br>And once again, he is raping our land. He has killed my chickens.<br>Now I can't fry them up. I was looking foward to my fried chicken :_:<br><br>His Roar is Monsterous. His eyes, bloodshot red. Even his Roar makes Innoruuk Tremble and fall to his knees in death.<br><br>His alligance is to no one. No one but hisself and his Greed. His Pride.<br><br>This Monster can appear in ths most demonic form..<br><br>Or he can be small. Cute. Cunning. A Handsome Man, Poor, crying out..<br>Crying out the words of Intolerance, Biggoty, and Racism.<br><br>WHERE THE FUCK WHAS YOUR TOLERANCE OF ME ON INNORUUK, YOU POWERGAMING SON OF A BITCH! WHERE!?<br><br>I have no sympathy for them. I shed no tear for you, Mr. Powergaming Man.<br><br>I have seen your horrors. I have felt the pain of your blade against my chest.<br><br>I have no sympathy. None at all.<br><br>I have seen you burn down our houses. I have seen you destroy our land. I have seen you beat and or turn our children into your minions.<br><br>I have no sympathy. None at all.<br><br>If I must be a Racist Biggot in your eyes, then so be it.<br><br>Even Verant has given up on us, the Oppressed Roleplayer.<br><br>But I will not give up on myself. <br>I am a Roleplayer.<br>Fuck you, Mr. Powergaming man.<br>Come and get me.<br><br>Their is no Salvation for us. No more.<br><br>I am going to roleplay till the end. I gave up on Innoruuk.<br>I gave up.<br><br>I will not give up here. You can't lie to me.<br><br>I've seen your tricks.<br>I've seen your horrors.<br><br>I've seen you, over the course of two years, effectivly take what was the Roleplayers, and Warp it into some Twisted sick demented game of your own.<br><br>Fuck you, Mr Roleplaying man.<br>Come and get me.<br><br>Vall, or whoever you are, be ready to lock this Thread. <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif">Shintou Shinai, A Follower of the Life, and Words of Lanys T'Vyl.Powergamers have EVERY OTHER server out there, maybe even the PvP servers..Can the roleplayers just get ..one?</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 1/17/02 7:41:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umollycat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mollycat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/17/02 5:47:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span cla