inds poetic beauty to shintou's rant.  Not bad at all, for a dark elf.  <br><br>Oh, come on! people....this is a rant board...let the man speak his mind.  People says he is a bigot, he has no tolerance, a nazi, and some even go as far as saying he is a racist.  Well, blade cuts both ways.  He call some of you powergamers, and he gets branded as an intolerant racist bigot nazi.  *shrug*  looks like both sides gets a stab at each other.<br><br>And Shintou....I understand your desire to keep the server as RP-pure as possible.  Trust me, coming from 6+ years of text based mud which is RP enforced (did I mention ppl can be deleted for inproper name?), i know exactly how you feel.  But EQ isn't any sort of traditional RP games.  ANYBODY can cough up the $10 monthly and can play at any server they want to.  You just gotta accept that this is by no means a perfect world, and work with what you got.   A milder tone of suggestion might work out better in the end. <br><br>RP or non-RP...FV is the only server I would ever chose to play.  I did not pay my $10 a month to hear people shouting &quot;reding 8!!!&quot; across the zone and basks in the glory that is him.  I did not pay $10 to be put on a waiting list to fight the orcs at Highpass.  I did not pay $10 to enter Crushbone only to find the zone is filled with lvl 30+ camping the warlord/trainer/emperor crush to farm items.  I did not pay my $10 to see Trolls, Ogres, dwarves, wood elves all grouped together in some happy little family way.<br><br>I came to FV for so many reasons that I cannot list them all here.  But I do know that my experience here in FV is the BEST i've ever had in EQ - great people (Rp'ers AND non-Rp'ers), friendly atmosphere (cept when Scratchy beat fanatically on my head <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ), an entirely too hilarious guild that I belong to, least amount of unpleasent exper